      public static boolean loadLibbulletjme(boolean dist, File directory, String buildType, String flavor)
      Load a Libbulletjme native library.
      Parameters:
      dist - true→distributed files, false→as-built files
      directory - (not null, readable, unaffected)
      buildType - "Debug" or "Release"
      flavor - "Sp", "SpMt", "SpMtQuickprof", "SpQuickprof", "Dp", or "DpMt"
      Returns:
      true after successful load, otherwise false
